title: All Play and No Work
description: Mega Man must resist the influence of a prankster bot named Chaotique, whose devil may care ideology appeals to the overworked superhero, until his friends pay the price for his dalliances.

title: Swing Set Jet Set
description: Axel and the team battle Princess SugarSalt for possession of Bearbarian's hammer, traded to her by one of their own - Galileo!

title: Know It All
description: When Vic accidently unleashes evil bats from a cave, it's up to the boys and Don to protect the town, but Vic's know-it-all attitude keeps getting in the way.

title: #LosConejosMágicos
description: Cuando Zee le pide a Kara que cuide a sus dos conejitos mágicos, pronto comienzan a multiplicarse y a desatar el caos por toda Metrópolis.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Thick as Thieves
description: Phil the Pilferer robs Vambre and Prohyas of their very best Magiswords so he can snag the Sheepy Mantis, but the Warriors find out that no Magisword is lame as they manage to keep Phil from becoming Thief of the Year.

title: The Crossroads Part 1
description: An attempt to use a derelict SpaceBridge sends The Ark to Unspace!

title: Time Share
description: Batman and Blue Beetle have to travel back in time to stop Chronos from destroying a young Dark Knight on his very first case.

title: Perder la cabeza
description: El equipo Tennyson se da una vuelta por una reunión familiar alternativa, y Ben se encuentra con mucho más que primos excéntricos, concretamente con Kevin 11 y los Hermanos Bicho, cuyo último invento alocado desata una serie de intercambios de cabeza divertidísimos entre todos los grupos.

title: El vagon de la piscina de pelotas
description: El grupo es confrontado por una nueva y extraña fuerza en una aventura por un vagón lleno de pelotas.

title: Separacion Rapida
description: Cuando una misteriosa tormenta eléctrica se abate sobre el Omni-Copter en el Ecuador, el equipo Tennyson pronto descubre que Solar y Polar están detrás del suceso.

title: Haunted Campfire
description: The campers must battle ghosts of their own creation after their scary stories mysteriously come true.

title: El vagon del pasado
description: Tulip se arriesga al confiar en un viejo enemigo.

title: Fistfull of Balloons
description: When Vic gets double-crossed during a water balloon fight, he goes on a revenge mission to find out who was responsible.

title: Parley Part 1
description: Megatron and Optimus parley in an attempt to unite against Starscream.

title: Memory Foam
description: When a new mattress sucks away all of Pizza Steve's memories, Uncle Grandpa and the crew must find a way to get them back.

title: Zombie King
description: Grundy escapes his Louisiana prison intent on using a magical crystal which will allow him to raise the dead from their graves. Only Batman and Swamp thing stand in the way of his growing zombie army.

title: Franken Pelea
description: Ben se sube al Rustbuggy para recibir una lección de conducción a lo largo de las dunas de Cabo Cod. Pero el plan da un extraño giro cuando el Rustbuggy se transforma en un monstruo motorizado por Bootleg, otra transformación alienígena de Kevin 11.

title: Felonious Prose
description: The Warrior mission of finding a lost contact lens gets seriously compromised from Vambre's obsession with the latest Veronica Victorious novel.

title: Last One Out of Beach City
description: Pearl, Steven and Amethyst go to a rock show.

title: While You Were Away
description: Dr. Psychobos and Princess Attea have invaded Rook's home planet Revonnah with an army of Incurseans! (Introducing new Ben alien, Astrodactyl.)

title: Los Jovenes Titanes vrum: primera parte
description: En este episodio de "Fuerza Turbo Titanes", los Titanes obtienen la habilidad de convertirse en autos.

title: Bring Me the Spark of Optimus Prime Part 1
description: The Decepticons compete to be the first to bring Megatron Optimus Prime's spark while Hot Rod chases the "Moon Cheetah."

title: Director's Cut
description: Oscar receives a camcorder from his parents and sets out to prove to them the magic on the island is real.

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: Cartoon Feud
description: Control Freak forces the Titans and the Scooby Gang to compete on Family Feud.

title: Fire Maker
description: The Ice Emperor learns of the ninja's arrival and sends his Blizzard Samurai warriors to destroy them and the villagers who sheltered them.

title: Bajo los reflectores
description: Cuando la reportera Verónica Venegas, madre de Lia, hace un reportaje acerca de Los Fantásticos, Strata El Cazador intenta capturar a Hydorous.

title: Cosmic Bupkiss
description: A storm blocks Oscar and Hedgehog's one chance to see a comet.

title: Hostile Take Over/The Big Bounce
description: Hostile Take Over: After more unsuccessful attempts to harness Core Cell energy the AO must battle their own Bakugan with AAAnimus tech in order to save them./The Big Bounce: The AO confront Philomena with concerns about her control over the Core Cell energy and are fired in the most unceremonious of manners.

title: The Break Up
description: A silly argument between Jeff and Sumo escalates until they vow never to speak to each other again. At first Clarence enjoys the separation, now he's always got someone to play with but eventually he becomes exhausted and must hatch a scheme to get the guys to be friends again.

title: A Rocky Start
description: The ninja have found their quest! Now they just have to get there, which involves a road trip through the Desert of Doom, a region supposedly inhabited by a giant scarab beetle.

title: A Small Problem
description: When Ben is not allowed on an attraction at a water park because he to short, he decides to go alien to get even with the ride's attendant.

title: Beyond the Grotto
description: In pursuit of a runaway Sea Lard, Finn and Jake are led down a whirlpool to a curious new land.

title: Bienvenido a la Zona Zombozo
description: Durante tiempos medievales, el equipo Tennyson debe esforzarse por recordar que no están en el pasado, sino en una feria renacentista, idonde el "Rey Zombozo" ha hipnotizado a sus invitados para que crean que viven en el pasado!

title: Bobbie Not Blobby
description: Axel discovers that the culprit behind Bobbie Blobby's missing mech-suit is Masko, who only wanted to clean out its clogged clay cannons, but lets the suit fall into the hands (or tentacles) of Dr. Nautilus - intent on flooding the sewers!

title: Ace of Squares
description: Craig vows to make the game of Four Square fun again by challenging its most dominant player!

title: El vagon de la playa
description: Tulip cierra un trato con una gata en un intento por volver a casa. ¿Acaso el precio vale la pena?

title: Sea of Tranquility Part 1
description: Optimus Prime and the Autobots battle Megatron and the Deceptions on Earth's Moon.

title: La Neblina del Paramo
description: El equipo Tennyson se hace internacional en el Omni-Copter, y la primera parada incluye una caminata por las Tierras Altas de Escocia. Pero el clima no es sólo malo, sino que hay niebla, y eso puede significa solamente una cosa: iel regreso de Niebla!

title: #TrianguloDeOdio
description: Cuando la exnovia de Hal aparece en el partido de bienvenida de la preparatoria Metrópolis y se enfurece por amor, convertida en la villana Star Sapphire, Jessica comienza a cuestionar sus propias tácticas no violentas.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Pleito animado
description: Control Fenómeno obliga a los Titanes y a la Scooby-pandilla a competir en Pleito Familiar.

title: Caza o Juego
description: Después de recibir un billete superexclusivo para Adrenalandia, Ben deja atrás al abuelo Max y a Gwen para disfrutar de las ventajas de ser el único asistente del parque. Pero pronto se entera de que no está solo.

title: Trials Part 1
description: Following the network of GroundBridges left by the Allspark, Optimus and Megatron finally discover the Allspark, and its Guardian, Cheetor.

title: A New Don
description: When Vic & Val discover that Don isn't really himself, it's up to them to use his kooky codex of conspiracies to save him.

title: Mao Mao's Bike Adventure
description: When Mao Mao underestimates enemy and friend alike, it almost costs him the entire kingdom.

title: Party Down Part 2
description: A malfunction in Wheeljack's party favors turns most of the Autobot crew feral, leaving Optimus, Cheetor, and Teletraan-X in a race to save their friends.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Cual Reloj?
description: Cuando una batalla con Kevin queda interrumpida, Ben se concentra en ser mejor que Gwen en el Campamento Espacial. Pero cuando Kevin regresa con la mirada extrañamente puesta en su prima, nuestro héroe debe descubrir quién está realmente detrás de todo esto: iCharmcaster!

title: Una leccion para todos
description: Los Fantásticos le enseñan a unos chicos del vecindario a no imitar a los demás. Por ejemplo, a quienes utilizan a sus Bakugan con fines frívolos.

title: Dungeons and Dayjobs
description: A botched mission leaves the Warriors in debt, so they take day jobs at Slugburger and sling Slugburgers for Witchy Simone!

title: Bloqueo de Tránsito
description: Cuando un paso elevado colapsa sobre la autopista, el equipo Tennyson queda varado en un embotellamiento junto con Simon Sez y familia. Pero cuando Ben y Simon se alían para enfrentar juntos al atasco, Simon solo consigue que las cosas sean mucho, pero mucho peores.

title: El poder interior
description: Masato Kazami vuelve junto con los guardaespaldas de la familia para llevar a Shun a Japón, pero esta vez, Shun y Hydorous tienen una sorpresa preparada.

title: Pegatrix
description: Lia no concuerda con las técnicas de Pegatrix, pero durante una intensa batalla, debe aprender a confiar en los conocimientos de su Bakugan.

title: Forever Road
description: During a drag race, Ben hopes to stay neck and neck with Vin Ethanol and La Grange as XLR8, but when his watch keeps shorting out, our hero must get creative if he is to keep up with his fast and furious foes!

title: Cat Burglar
description: An alarmingly familiar cat burglar terrorizes Townsville.

title: Game of Masks
description: As Lloyd and Harumi search the Oni Temple for the last mask, the ninja are taken hostage and discover Princess Harumi's true intentions.

title: Jail Break
description: Steven teams up with a new ally to rescue the Gems.

title: True Potential
description: Just when the Ninja think they have saved the day, Lord Garmadon returns to Ninjago, and frees Harumi, who encourages him to "achieve his true potential" by conquering the one thing that has always stood in his way, his son, Lloyd.

title: The Belly of the Beast
description: To repair the Land-Bounty, the ninja must retrieve a critical engine component that has been swallowed by a giant scarab beetle.

title: Churro Kings
description: When Vic & Val start making good money from selling churros at the taco stand, their lust for stuff makes them do dirty tricks to take out their competition.

title: Burrito
description: Grizz likes Burritos. A lot. So much so that after a restaurant makes a Bear-Sized Burrito, Grizz can't bring himself to eat such a majestic work of art. He carries the burrito everywhere making it a new and increasingly smelly part of his life.

title: I Am the Allspark Part 2
description: Optimus seemingly sacrifices himself to get the Allspark back from Starscream, leaving the rest of the Autobots to deal with Megatron.

title: La Celula Nucleo
description: Los Fantásticos defienden la Célula Núcleo de un ataque de Tiko, y en el último intento de Dan por salvarla, él y Drago logran liberar un nuevo poder.

title: Bad Bad Cop
description: Vambre and Prohyas pretend to be cops in their attempts to shakedown a dangerous bunch of pirates to find a broccoli smuggler.

title: Demonios internos
description: Los Fantásticos encuentran la forma de salir de Vestroia, pero descubren que en realidad están en un mundo paralelo.

title: #SweetJustice Part 4
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Teen Titans Vroom: Part 2
description: In the exciting conclusion of "Turbo Titans Go Force" the Titans must learn to work together to stop Dr. Military.

title: Let's Be Friends
description: KO wants to become friends with Enid and Rad and get hired at Lakewood Plaza Turbo.

title: Our Stuff
description: After the bears play a little pickup basketball (they're very bad), they go back to grab their stuff by the side of the court only to find it's been stolen!  The Bears race across town trying to track down their stuff and end up cracking a giant case in the process.

title: Follow Your Dreams
description: Apple and Onion need to find a dream to follow, so that their lives don't head nowhere.

title: Bebe Baktu
description: Cuando es atacado en la jungla, el equipo Tennyson es salvado por un niño que se parece inquietantemente a Tim Buktu, pero cuando descubren que realmente es una versión en miniatura del infame trotamundos, Ben sabe que se avecina otra amenaza, Nanny Nightmare!

title: Last Laugh
description: Ben's fear of clowns emerges at an unfortunate time when our heroes stumble upon a wicked circus with a psychic vampire clown named Zomobozo.

title: Lil' Mac
description: Mr. Gus' nephew terrorizes Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve.

title: El Bentatlon
description: El equipo Tennyson se dirige a la verdadera Grecia en el Omni-Copter. Pero cuando de repente son capturados por el Caballero por Siempre a mitad de vuelo, Ben termina en un coliseo, donde se enfrenta a algunos viejos enemigos.

title: Curses/Bang for Your Buck
description: Curses: When Bubbles overhears the Professor saying some bad words, the girls add a whole new slew of adjectives to their vocabulary./Bang for Your Buck: When the girls and the Gangreen Gang discover a destructo ray for sale at Mojo's Yard Sale, each team sets out to see who can earn the most money and buy it first.

title: More More More!
description: In order to out-muscle Guts Man, Mega Man copies the big bot's schematics, and his insatiable appetite!

title: Que ocurre con Dan
description: Cuando Dan se comporta de forma extraña con los Fantásticos, Lightning olfatea la verdad: iUn impostor!

title: Doorway to Helen
description: Craig makes a long distance connection with a kid that loves the creek as much as he does.

title: La sed de poder
description: Tras una discusión entre Wynton y Dan, el coronel Tripp controla la mente de Wynton para que ataque la ciudad con Lupitheon. Esto inicia una guerra entre Los Fantásticos y el ejército.

title: Dead Man's Squall
description: Zane's near demise at the hands of Mr. E forces the ninja to flee aboard the Bounty, where they discover that a transmission Zane intercepted may reveal the hidden location of the Quiet One.

title: Sale el Don
description: Cuando Vic y Val descubren que Don Jalapeño no es realmente él mismo, depende de ellos usar el alocado libro de conspiraciones de Don para salvarlo.

title: Los reyes de los Churros
description: Cuando Vic y Val comienzan a hacer dinero con la venta de churros en el puesto de tacos, su deseo por objetos los obliga a emplear trucos sucios para eliminar a la competencia.

title: El baul de los recuerdos
description: Al ser confrontada por China Riot, Lia logra evolucionar a Pegatrix cuando comprende la verdadera razón de su obsesión por las cámaras.

title: Presentando a Kevin 11
description: En un encuentro de intercambio local, Ben se interesa en un coleccionable de Luchadores de Sumo. Pero cuando Kevin se apodera del objeto, nuestro héroe debe superar el arma secreta de Kevin para recuperarlo: iun 11º extraterrestre!

title: Dark Birth Part 1
description: While Starscream acquires new power through the Allspark, the Autobots mistakenly assume Starscream is still under Megatron's command.

title: The Never Gwending Story
description: When Chef loses the last page of the story-time book, Gwen takes over and creates a monster that all the kids start to believe in.

title: Ghost Town Part 1
description: When Windblade mysteriously steals the Allspark, Optimus, Bumblebee, Hot Rod and Cheetor follow her to a strange abandoned city.

title: Get Back Jojo
description: Mojo goes back in time to try and stop the Professor from having the inspiration for the perfect little girls. Little does he know that in doing so he provides just the spark the young Professor needs.

title: La noche que Ben Tennyson vino al pueblo
description: El equipo Tennyson viaja a Wheeler, "la ciudad minera más animada de la Ruta 66". Pero cuando Ben se pone paranoico con la idea de que el Caballero por Siempre lo esté persiguiendo, debe tratar de convencer a su familia al mismo tiempo que evita que su nuevo enemigo destruya la ciudad.

title: Access Denied
description: When Axel and the team try to figure out what Sarge Charge's secret weapon is, they get ejected from the house by his newly upgraded security system and must fight their way back inside before Madcap does.

title: #SweetJustice Part 3
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Beware the Scare-Crow
description: During a visit to the farm of Penny Bennyson's grandfather, Team Tennyson is constantly haunted by a Scare-Crow that's come to life, but when Ben discovers that Aristocrow is behind it all, our hero must defeat Aristocrow's master, the steam-powered Steam Smythe, if he is to save his cousin's farm!

title: Perdidas y ganancias
description: Un promotor llamado Everett Ray quiere convencer a Los Fantásticos de ingresar a una liga oficial de Batallas Bakugan.

title: Water Park
description: The trio heads to Squirty's Moist Mountain water park, and as Clarence learns the truth about his idol Squirty, Jeff and Sumo wait in line for the reopening of the parks tallest slide, The Curd Churner.

title: Rey del Castillo
description: Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max viajan al Castillo Bishopbrook para visitar a un pariente lejano de la realeza. Pero cuando Ben se encuentra con un "fantasma" en la casa embrujada, resulta ser su nuevo rival, Kevin 11, que lanza a alienígenas aún más retorcidos en su camino: iThornblade, Undertow y Materia Oscura!

title: Secret Science Part 1
description: While studying the scraplets Wheeljack is kidnapped by Shockwave who tries to enlist Wheeljack's help.

title: #ConoceAGuepardo
description: Barbara Minerva está super celosa de la "pequeña señorita perfecta" Diana Prince. Pero cuando usa un antiguo artefacto de la colección de su padre para lanzar una maldición contra Diana, la maldición se vuelve en su contra.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Un almuerzo inesperado
description: Cuando el Restaurante de Hamburguesas es amenazado por un violento Bakugan, Dan llega para salvar el día...y las hamburguesas.

title: Plaza Film Festival
description: When the plaza has its own film festival, KO, Enid and Rad are sure their entry will win!

title: Stratificados
description: Los Fantásticos emprenden una misión en el misterioso mundo laberíntico de Vestroia para buscar a Strata El Cazador y liberar a los Bakugan que tiene presos.

title: Malos actores
description: Alguien expone a Dan por mentir acerca de la evolución de Drago, mientras el equipo se enfrenta a Duran Dane y su desdichado Bakugan, Nillious.

title: Cool Bikes
description: Mordecai and Rigby want cool bikes because if their bikes are cool, then they are cool.

title: El vagon de cristal
description: Tulip, Atticus y Uno-Uno entran a un vagón con un bosque de cristal y deben participar en un ritual musical.

title: Esto llega hasta el Once
description: Durante una última parada en una juguetería antes del viaje inaugural de Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max a través del Atlántico, Ben se encuentra con su antiguo bravucón, Kevin 11, que ahora tiene nuevos poderes. Es capaz de transformarse en alienígenas al igual que Ben, como el doble "pirata" de Cannonbolt: iWreckingbolt!

title: Atrapados en la jungla
description: Aún perdidos en Vestroia, Los Fantásticos experimentan los efectos de la Célula Núcleo que altera sus cuerpos, y se encuentran cara a cara con el monstruo Bakugan, Tiko.

title: Snake Jaguar
description: In order to join the Sons of Garmadon, Zane (aka Snake Jaguar) participates in a deadly motorcycle initiation race.

title: Perfect Storm Part 2
description: Arcee and Grimlock get an adventure they never bargained for as they protect the helpless Ark from all manner of space anomalies.

title: Encantadas
description: Durante una comida familiar en un campamento forestal, Charmcaster usa su magia para cambiar de lugar con Gwen, pero cuando Ben descubre a "Charmcaster" husmeando, ataca, sin darse cuenta de que en realidad es su hechizada prima.

title: Follow that Space Cab!
description: While Superman escorts his prisoner Mr. Mind between planets, he is attacked by Lobo who wants to collect a reward on Mind. Temporarily powered-down, Superman seeks Space Cabbie's help to get away from Lobo.

title: Hogar, dulce hogar
description: Los Fantásticos vuelven a casa y se dan cuenta de que el tiempo no ha pasado. Pronto descubren que su conocimiento acerca de las batallas ha aumentado de forma exponencial.

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: Prey or Play
description: After receiving a super-exclusive ticket to Adrenaland, Ben leaves behind Grandpa Max and Gwen to enjoy the perks of being the parks only attendant, but when he learns he's not alone, our hero must now contend with the only kid who could afford the price of admission: Billy Billions!

title: Balance
description: Ms. Baker introduces a new student, a short little kid with a hook for a hand named Balance. Clarence is pumped to have a new friend, despite Balance's gruff attitude and snarky jibes at the other kids. When Clarence discovers a disturbing secret about Balance, he and Belson team up to expose him for who he truly is.

title: No lo digas y Hazlo
description: Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max llegan a un parque nacional nativo americano para conocer los plintos de Ayasha, una antigua formación rocosa parecida a la de Stonehenge. Pero cuando llega el siniestro hechicero Hex, iBen debe luchar contra una bestia que Hex hizo mágicamente con rocas enormes!

title: Bird Boy Man
description: Sumo discovers an injured roadrunner, names him Hot Sauce, and nurses him back to health. The two become inseparable pals, but Sumo learns that a wild animal can't be contained.

title: Bad Moon Rising Part 2
description: The Autobots work to stop the Moon from crashing into the Earth as Starscream must reckon with betraying Megatron.

title: All Good in the Wood
description: When Suna and Ashley's science project turns into a hungry blob monster, Mega Man must team up with Wood Man to shut down the experiment gone wrong before it devours the city!

title: El hijo prodigo
description: Mientras los Fantásticos intentan evolucionar a sus Bakugan como lo hizo Dan con Drago, el primo de Shun, Masato, llega a la ciudad para llevarlo de regreso a Japón.

title: Viral Video
description: The Bears think they have what it takes to make and star in a viral video, but when Nom-Nom decides that they don't, Grizz breaks into the koala's limo in an effort to change his mind.

title: Pizza Eve
description: Uncle Grandpa falls for Pizza Steve's "girlfriend" and ends up in serious danger.

title: Bromas pesadas
description: Las constantes bromas pesadas de Wynton colman la paciencia de su Bakugan, Trox, quien decide darle una lección.

title: Perfect Storm Part 1
description: Arcee and Grimlock go off on an adventure only to return and discover the Ark without power and their friends all in stand-by mode.

title: Positive Attitude Theory
description: Apple and Onion spend a day in Falafel's shoes and use their positive attitude to prove he shouldn't be so grumpy.

title: Enredos perrunos
description: Lightning descubre un nuevo Bakugan, Artulean, y eso desata una fuerte rivalidad entre él y Howlkor.

title: Awesome vs. AAAnimus
description: Awesome V Aaanimus, Part 1: The AO plan on sneaking into AAAnimus and rescuing their Bakugan but are stopped by Benton who offers up an alternate plan./Awesome V Aaanimus, Part 2: The AO team up with Benton Dusk to recapture their stolen Bakugan and free the energy from the Mind Core Cell under the control of AAAnimus.

title: #AdventuresInBunnysitting
description: Zee asks Kara to look after her two magical bunnies, which quickly start to multiply, wreaking havoc all across Metropolis.

title: Trials Part 2
description: Cheetor attempts to judge whether Optimus or Megatron are more worthy of the Allspark, but an unexpected visitor dashes all the bots' plans.

title: El atrapador
description: Dan y Wynton se encuentran con la posible ubicación secreta de la Célula Núcleo, y con el coronel Tripp, que busca apoderarse de la fuente de energía.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Infinite Vendetta Part 1
description: The Autobots and Decepticons are surprised by the return of their long-lost comrades, Jetfire and Skybyte.

title: Molestando a los Bichos
description: El equipo de Tennyson viaja al Instituto Crisalín en busca de yoga a altas temperaturas y buenas vibraciones, solo para descubrir que los hermanos Bicho también están de vacaciones. Pero ¿los astutos insectoides están realmente de vacaciones, o están tramando otro de sus tontos planes?

title: Sr. Luna
description: Wynton encuentra un nuevo Bakugan que resulta difícil de controlar, y las cosas se complican cuando el Coronel Tripp se apodera de Trox.

title: High Flying Hostiles/Backfire Brawl
description: High Flying Hostiles: While escorting the Mind Core Cell to AAAnimus Campus, the AO are attacked by Masato Kazami and his Body Guards./Backfire Brawl: Philomena's attempt to refocus the Mind Core Cell's power backfires and the AO must fight their fellow employees inside the AAAnimus Campus.

title: Fallen Arches/The Mane Event
description: Fallen Arches: When a gang of old-time villains come out of retirement, the girls enlist the best superhero team of the past to save the city./The Mane Event: Bubbles and Buttercup are playing with Blossom's beautiful locks when an accident happens. Now, Blossom is too embarrassed to put up a good fight.

title: The Visitor Part 1
description: Bumblebee searches for any information his fellow Autobots might have regarding a strange creature he saw on the Moon.

title: Teen Titans Vroom: Part 1
description: In this episode of "Turbo Titans Go Force" the Titans gain the ability to transform into cars.

title: Starscream's Children Part 2
description: Starscream reveals his scraplet army, incapacitating the Autobots and Decepticons and setting up a show down between him and Cheetor.

title: Las Garras del Gato
description: Mientras disfruta de las vistas y los sonidos de un festival de música, Ben se eriza ante la sugerencia de Gwen de ser su nueva compañera, ya que el festival está amenazado por las ondas sonoras supersónicas de Lord Decibel.

title: El vagon de los Corgi
description: Tulip y Uno-Uno exploran un vagón lleno de Corgis y se enfrentan a un misterioso monstruo.

title: Omnicoptero
description: Cuando el ingeniero Phil Billings, amigo del Abuelo Max, le regala al equipo Tennyson el Omni-Copter, un vehículo volador de última generación que puede transportar el Rustbucket hasta aventuras en el extranjero, Vapor Smythe sube a los cielos para obligar a aterrizar el primer vuelo de prueba de Ben y su familia. Pero sin que nuestros héroes lo sepan, Smythe fue enviado a combatir las formas alienígenas más nuevas de Ben por un misterioso y poderoso enemigo: el Caballero por Siempre.

title: The Check
description: Gumball, Darwin and Anais are delighted when Grandpa Louie gives them a check for $5000. They immediately start fantasizing over what to spend it on. But when Mom and Dad say they're going to spend the money on paying bills instead, it's a race to the bank to see who can cash the check first.

title: Iced Out
description: Madcap's latest creation, the Ice Crusher, puts the whole city in a deep freeze, forcing Axel and the team to face him in a game of high-stakes hockey or risk slip-sliding into another ice age!

title: I Heart Heartforde
description: Oscar, hedgehog and the other campers are excited to take a trip to the non-magical town of Heartforde.

title: La Grange Muralla
description: Ben, Gwen y el abuelo Max hacen un viaje a la Gran Muralla, pero su aventura por poco termina arruinada por los temerarios LaGrange y Vin Etanol, que intentan saltar sobre el monumento internacional. Ben debe subirse al Rustbuggy para ahuyentar a los enemigos.

title: Los Jovenes Titanes vrum: segunda parte
description: En la emocionante conclusión de "Fuerza Turbo Titanes", los Titanes deben aprender a trabajar juntos para detener al Doctor Militar.

title: Escape From Earth Part 2
description: With the Ark extricated from Mt. St. Hilary, the Autobots must run the gauntlet of Decepticon forces to escape Earth with the Allspark.

title: Padres y amigos
description: Osamu Kazami viene para llevarse a su hijo Shun a casa y se encuentra con un obstáculo que no había contemplado.

title: Sea of Tranquility Part 2
description: The Autobots struggle to stop the Decepticon's planet-cracking weapon as it targets Earth.

title: Attack of Thermometron 9000
description: Axel must wrangle Galileo and Bobbie to shut down a rogue thermostat - improperly upgraded by Slobot - as it plunges the house into extreme hot and cold zones.

title: We Messed Up
description: KO, Rad and Enid accidentally break one of Mr. Gar's prized possessions!

title: Jean Jacket
description: The Bears find a bedazzled jean jacket in a dumpster. It's just about the coolest thing they've ever seen and seems to make the wearer of the jacket extremely lucky. But after the Bears fight over who gets control of the jacket, they have to consider that their denim blessing has become a curse.

title: #LaCubetaDeBurritos
description: A Babs le encanta su trabajo en el restaurante de comida rápida "La Cubeta de Burritos" , pero a su jefe, que está harto de que ella siempre llegue tarde y de su enorme dispersión, le encantaría encontrar cualquier excusa para despedirla. Cuando se produce un robo a un banco que está enfrente de su trabajo, Babs no puede decidir si encarnar su papel de superheroína o el de empleada obediente de La Cubeta. Pero ¿será capaz de salvar a todos y conservar su empleo justo a tiempo?
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Cirque-Us
description: After saving a State University Alumni ribbon cutting ceremony, Ben becomes the guest of honor at the upcoming Gala, but when the cirque entertainment turns out be Zombozo, in disguise, Ben must not only defeat the evil clown but his mysterious new sidekick, Pirouette!

title: Paseo en Buggy
description: Después de ganar un cinturón como campeón de Luchadores de Sumo, Ben regresa al Rustbucket y encuentra su premio en los brazos de Kevin. Pero cuando su rival secuestra el Rustbuggy, inuestro héroe no debe detenerse ante nada para recuperar lo que le pertenece legítimamente!

title: Parley Part 2
description: The Autobot-Decepticon peace talks breaks down after Slipstream returns with a dire warning.

title: Aventura en el laberinto
description: Perdidos en el laberinto de Vestroia, Los Fantásticos se enfrentan a poderosas fuerzas que parecen luchar por el control del planeta.

title: Tummy Trouble
description: When the Incursean armada kidnaps the Gourmand Queen, Ben and Rook must get the warring Gormand factions to work together to save her and stop the Incursean invasion.

title: Kevin 11
description: After a big argument with Max, Ben rebels by going out on his own in the Big Apple and makes friends with Kevin 11, who has plans for the Omnitrix.

title: Breehn Ho
description: Avast mateys! Clarence and Sumo are psyched to play their pirate-themed board game, Thirty Days and Seven Seas, until they learn Jeff has invited boring old Breehn along. After Breehn gets frustrated and leaves, it's up to the three scallywags to rescue Breehn from an intense flood.

title: Convencion de Rath
description: De regreso en casa, Ben no puede inscribirse en un concurso de cosplay de gatos sin su propio disfraz. Pero cuando se convierte en Rath, un nuevo alienígena con aspecto felino y mal carácter, el lado salvaje que Ben acaba de descubrir pronto tendrá resultados inesperados.

title: Cirque-Ados
description: Ben es el invitado de honor de una gala, pero cuando el espectáculo del circo resulta ser Zombozo disfrazado, Ben no solo debe derrotar al malvado payaso, sino también a su misterioso nuevo compañero, iPirueta!

title: #LaDulceJusticia - Primera parte
description: En el episodio estreno de cuatro partes de la serie, seis chicas comunes y corrientes se conocen y descubren que tienen poderes extraordinarios. Deciden unir sus fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: El miedo de Strata
description: Los Fantásticos resuelven la misteriosa desaparición del Bakugan de un niño, y conocen a un cazador de Bakugan llamado Strata.

title: Bring Me the Spark of Optimus Prime Part 2
description: Slipstream searches for her missing Seekers while Hot Rod's "Moon Cheetah" chase brings him unexpectedly aboard the Nemesis.

title: Love at First Bite
description: Val crushes on a girl named Matty, who Vic is suspicious of but Val ignores his warnings. When Val goes to dinner at her house she turns into a Matlazihua and he discovers he's what's for dinner!

title: Cuatro por Cuatro
description: Durante su visita a Ciudad Gemelos, Ben y Gwen se inscriben en una competencia de laser-tag. Pero cuando Ben se une a Kevin, los dos deben superar sus diferencias si quieren terminar en la cima.

title: Champions of Breakfast
description: An epic battle between Vambre and her Waffle Magisword and Prohyas' Pancake Magisword escalates to a war that can only end when Grup solicits his Cave Weirdo pals to be peacemakers.

title: Industrias Dusk Parte 1
description: Los Fantásticos conocen a Benton Dusk y descubren que su pequeño mundo está a punto de volverse mucho más grande.

title: Una verdad a medias
description: Un críptico correo electrónico lleva a Los Fantásticos en busca de un Bakugan desaparecido, pero pronto se dan cuenta de que el correo era una prueba de un misterioso benefactor.

title: The Visitor Part 2
description: Dino-Mode Grimlock careens out-of-control around the Ark after drinking Wheeljack's hyper-fuel.

title: Dream Scheme/You Snooze, You Lose
description: Dream Scheme: The Sandman would like a little rest so he puts the world to sleep. The girls must battle him in his dreams to get things back to normal./You Snooze, You Lose: When the Amoeba Boys find Mojo's plan to destroy the Powerpuff Girls, the girls unwittingly help them build a machine for their own destruction.

title: #SweetJustice Part 2
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Collect Them All
description: After the other Titans are turned into collectibles and disappear, Robin must search yard sales and stores to find them.

title: Una extrana conexion
description: Drago lidera a los Bakugan contra la amenaza de Tiko, para proteger una poderosa fuente de energía.

title: Ultraclops
description: Badgerclops gets huge to destroy a towering monster, but when he refuses to shrink down, the kingdom faces a new terror.

title: El bravucon
description: Los Fantásticos deben lidiar con un bravucón que usa a su Bakugan para intimidar a los chicos del vecindario.

title: The Climb
description: Craig's phone gets stuck in Mt. Sycamore, the tallest tree in the creek!

title: Cabeza de Playa
description: Después de viajar a Tampa Beach, Florida, el equipo Tennyson espera poder descansar y relajarse, pero las tempestades sin temperamento, los Climáticos, tienen otros planes que Ben debe frustrar: iconstruir una nueva base en la playa!

title: Invasion of the Booger Snatchers
description: Harold believes that the picture day photographer is somehow turning the kids into well behaved zombies.

title: Mascara de poder
description: Philomena Dusk, de la Corporación AAAnimus, contrata a Magnus y le implanta un dispositivo que aumenta el poder de su Bakugan para derrotar a Dan.

title: Huelga por el Botin
description: Mientras Phil y el abuelo Max afinan el Omni-Copter, Ben, inquieto, saca el Rustbuggy de la carretera. Pero cuando de repente es capturado por Tetrax, nuestro héroe no solo debe escapar, sino también evitar la ira de los traicioneros Kraab y SeiSeis.

title: Rad
description: With Plumber agents trapped in Incursean territory, Ben and Rook must employ the services of Rad Dudesman, the roughest, toughest smuggler in the galaxy.  (Introducing Rad Dudesman, return of classic Ben alien, Eye Guy.)

title: The Jade Princess
description: In the wake of a vicious attack upon the palace, the Sons of Garmadon steal the second Oni Mask, and the ninja invite the royal princess, Harumi, into their makeshift family.

title: Carretera por Siempre
description: Durante una carrera de aceleración, Ben espera mantenerse al mismo nivel con Vin Etanol y La Grange como XLR8. Pero cuando su reloj hace cortocircuito una y otra vez, nuestro héroe debe ser creativo si quiere seguir el ritmo de sus rápidos y furiosos enemigos.

title: Prank War
description: When Master Frown starts a prank war with UniKingdom, the friends are ready to strike back. But Unikitty doesn't really understand pranks, thinking they're too mean. Can the friends help Unikitty comprehend a proper goof and win the prank war with Frown? Or will they be forced to suffer his tricks without retaliation and admit defeat?

title: Party Down Part 1
description: On their way to back to Cybertron, the Autobots attempt to have some well-deserved fun by throwing a party.

title: The Dynamo Dynamic
description: Axel finds himself at the center of a disagreement between Sarge and Masko over what's more important in battle - the weapon or the one who wields it - after Dynamo bonds the trio together!

title: El Origen de las Especies Parte 1
description: Dan conoce a su pareja Bakugan, Drago, por primera vez y nos enteramos del "incidente" que ocurrió en la Tierra hace doce años.

title: The Quiet One
description: As Lloyd and Harumi venture deep into Primeval's Eye in search of the third Oni Mask, the ninja attempt to fix the Bounty and make a startling discovery.

title: Bad Moon Rising Part 1
description: Starscream makes a play for leadership of the Deceptions as the Autobots storm the Decepticon's Moon Base.

title: Gum and Gummer
description: Beth gets her gum stuck in Leshawna's hair and has to get it out - without Leshawna finding out it's there.

title: Safety First
description: Concerned about Puppycorn's propensity to hurt himself constantly, the gang places him into Richard's old Safety Suit. The suit does indeed keep him safe, but when Puppycorn purposefully puts himself in danger the suit goes into lock down, and won't allow him to move. Now the gang must figure out a way to get him out of the Safety Suit.

title: Cuidado con el espantapajaros
description: Durante una visita a la granja del abuelo de Penny Bennyson, un espantapájaros que cobró vida gracias a Aristocuervo persigue constantemente al equipo Tennyson.

title: Industrias Dusk Parte 2
description: Benton Dusk revela que Los Fantásticos son considerados personas de interés por poderosas corporaciones como AAAnimus.

title: Kazami Family Feud/Greatest of the Kazami
description: Kazami Family Feud: Masato attacks, but the AO soon realize that Ichiro is keeping a Golden Bakugan captive, forcing them to choose between the lesser of two evils!/Greatest of the Kazami: Shun makes an impassioned plea to Ichiro, but it is too late as the Kazami compound is overrun by Bakuzon and the Visvus Cell is lost.

title: Grande en Japón
description: Durante un recorrido por el Museo de Robótica Japonés, Ben encuentra a Tim Buktu, un héroe que fue por el mal camino, "tratando de salvar" a Tokio de un Dragón. ¿Tim cambió por fin o este no es más que otro de sus planes mal concebido para hacer el papel de héroe?

title: Cool Bro Bots
description: Mordecai and Rigby confront robots.

title: Sin tocar
description: El equipo Tennyson visita un Museo de Samurái en Tokio, donde Ben está demasiado impaciente para esperar la experiencia de caligrafía, ya que la experiencia de samurái suena más divertida. Pero cuando alguien roba una peligrosa espada samurái de la exposición, Ben debe enfrentarse a su ladrón: el nuevo gran malvado de la ciudad, el Caballero por Siempre.

title: Film Flam
description: A sleazy director arrives in Townsville to make a film about the Powerpuff Girls. But this Hollywood type wants more out of Townsville than an Oscar-winning film.

title: Carter and Briggs
description: Mordecai and Rigby enter a donut contest to win a cameo on their favorite cop show.

title: Blank Eyed Girl
description: One very spooky night, Finn and Jake come face-to-face with an urban myth.

title: #LaDulceJusticia - Tercera parte
description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 3 del episodio estreno.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Billy Billones
description: En Aspen, Colorado, Ben, Gwen y el abuelo Max van de excursión para encontrar al Olvideti. Pero cuando se encuentran con la pista artificial de esquí de Billy Billones, Ben debe luchar contra Billy con la ayuda del propio Olvideti.

title: Unboxing Part 1
description: Axel ventures into his uncle's strictly off-limits basement lab in hopes of fixing a broken toy and ends up unleashing living ones instead: the renegade Madcap and a whole team of superpowered toys dedicated to stopping him!

title: The Perfect Adventure
description: When Mao Mao gets hungry for the perfect adventure, Adorabat tells a white lie.

title: Melter Skelter
description: When Chef tells Beth he won't buy the new super amazing toy she wants because they already have plenty to play with, she goes on a mission to get rid of their toys.

title: Cyber Luchadores
description: En Biggie Box Japón, Ben espera en una fila épica el lanzamiento de Cyber Luchadores, el último videojuego de Luchadores de Sumo. Pero muy pronto, Ben debe salvar la tienda: no de los clientes ansiosos por comprar el juego sino de Vapor Smythe, ique quiere modernizar un mecanismo gigantesco con sus vandálicos poderes de vapor!

title: Let's Be Heroes
description: When KO tags along with his mom to work, he discovers the convenience store next door is his key to becoming a great hero.

title: All Trick No Treat
description: On Halloween, Axel gets too caught up in the scares and loses track of the fun - just in time for an infiltration by the worst trick 'r' treater of all, Madcap!

title: Nacion Xingo
description: Kevin 11 aumenta la potencia de Xingo -que queda libre y causa estragos en otros programas de televisión-, y Ben es el responsable de detener a los dos.

title: Un golpe de ternura
description: Después de derrotar a Strata, Los Fantásticos se dan cuenta de que no volvieron solos, sino con un Bakugan parecido a un panda que les dará muchos problemas.

title: Maiz Peleas
description: El equipo Tennyson descubre una reconstrucción del conflicto familiar Hartfield-McJoy en el maizal de al lado, pero cuando Hex resucita a los fantasmas de las verdaderas familias enemistadas, Ben debe encontrar la manera de reunirlos si quiere salvar a todos.

title: Insomnio en el Sena
description: Durante su estadía en París, Francia, Ben descubre a Zombozo en pleno robo en el Louvre. Pero cuando Zombozo hipnotiza a Ben para que se quede sin palabras, Ben debe navegar por una tierra extranjera como un mimo para detener al payaso criminal y su circo ambulante.

title: Electric Buttercup
description: Buttercup gets more than she bargained for when she makes a deal with a cool '80s metalhead to get a sweet new guitar.

title: Showdown Part I
description: The Faction infiltrates Galvan in an attempt to destroy Azmuth.  (Introducing new Nemetrix aliens Omnivoracious & Vicetopus.)

title: Bonnie & Neddy
description: Finn and Jake, acting on orders from Candy Kingdom's new ruler Princess King of Ooo, stumble upon one of the kingdom's greatest secrets.

title: Spotted Part 1
description: Worried about finding a useful position among the Autobots, Cheetor learns how to become an Autobot Scout from Bumblebee.

title: Escape From Earth Part 1
description: Optimus struggles to recover from using the Matrix of Leadership while the Autobots attempt to get the Allspark back to Cybertron.

title: Wiped Out Part 2
description: Separated from his friends, Cheetor is captured by the territorial Sharkticons who enlist him in their fight over the last remaining bits of their destroyed planet.

title: The Never-Realm
description: The ninja arrive in the Never-Realm where they quickly find themselves overwhelmed. Luckily, they are taken in by a tribe of Ice Fishers who tell them Zane has been imprisoned by the evil Ice Emperor.

title: The Choices
description: When a typically stressful Watterson family dinner pushes her to the edge of her sanity, Nicole starts reminiscing about the time she met Richard. Might her life have been better if she'd never stopped to talk to her future husband and taken a different path instead?

title: Fire Man in the Hole
description: While hiking on a dormant volcano, Aki sets out to retrieve Ashley's lost camera and, as Mega Man, to stop Fire Man from setting off an eruption!

title: The Black Market Car
description: Mirror Tulip tries to create a new life for herself outside the Mirror World.

title: Not Funny
description: With their 6 month friend anniversary approaching, Apple has to find a way not to lose his best friend.

title: Our Ugly Selves/Trhyno Lives!
description: Our Ugly Selves: Abandoned in the Vestroia Labyrinth, the AO must deal with their personal losses and, worse, the Bakuzoned Awful Ones!/Trhyno Lives!: When the AO and Magnus form an alliance to free the Golden Bakugan, their differences lead to a horrible sacrifice for Dan and Lia.

title: Cheep Thrills
description: After finding a baby monster in the park, Bubbles insists on adopting it without considering the consequences!

title: The Frogs of War Part 2
description: With Ben missing, the Incurseans now control the Earth. It's up to Rook and the remaining Plumbers to lead the resistance and fight back! (Introducing new Ben alien, Bullfrag.)

title: El Chupacabro
description: El equipo Tennyson descubre que las cabras de una pequeña aldea están siendo aterrorizadas por el legendario Chupacabra. Pero cuando Ben se da cuenta de que en realidad se trata del Dr. Ánimo, nuestro héroe debe frustrar al malvado médico.

title: The Last Kid in the Creek
description: A terrible curse leaves Craig as the only kid in the creek.

title: El Origen de las Especies Parte 2
description: Dan y sus amigos ganan la Batalla Bakugan, demostrando que los Fantásticos son nuestros héroes y los mejores Peleadores Bakugan.

title: La locomotora
description: Tulip logra llegar al frente del tren y debe afrontar una decisión.

title: Kiki's Pizza Delivery Service
description: Steven saves Kiki from some delicious nightmares.

title: Apple's Short
description: Apple needs to be tall so that he can be in love.

title: The Bentathlon
description: After stuffing their faces with gyros, Team Tennyson makes their way to the real Greece in the Omni-Copter, but when they are suddenly captured by the Forever Knight mid-flight, Ben ends up in a coliseum, where he is pit against old foes: Iron Kyle, Queen Bee, and the Ground Hawgs!

title: Ene-amigos
description: Dos nuevos Peleadores Bakugan, Shun y Magnus, buscan ser parte de Los Fantásticos.

title: El vagon inacabado
description: El grupo entra a un vagón sin terminar e intenta arreglarlo.

title: Unboxing Part 2
description: Axel discovers that he can transform into a toy and teams up with his new team of toys to stop Madcap from stealing a Minergy battery.

title: NEW IN 2020 TRAILER
description: A brand-new year is on the horizon, and it's packed full of new episodes from the shows you love.

title: El vagon cuadriculado
description: Tulip, una obstinada niña de 13 años, encuentra un misterioso tren donde cada vagón contiene su propio universo.

title: Face Your Fears
description: Apple and Onion must face their fears while trapped in a pet shop, so they can save French Fry from facing hers.

title: Tutores Bakugan
description: Dan y Wynton conocen a un extraño chico que los lleva a un laberinto subterráneo, donde descubren que el Bakugan del chico ha sido esclavizado.

title: El equipo Exit
description: Los Fantásticos compiten por el número de visitas en sus videos con un equipo rival llamado "El equipo Exit" en una batalla donde se juegan el todo por el todo.

title: Y Xingo era su Nombre
description: Cuando la nueva aplicación Xingo aparece misteriosamente en la tableta de Gwen, Ben no puede evitarlo y la activa a pesar de la desaprobación de su prima. Así, lanza una trampa que transporta a Ben al mundo animado y a Xingo de vuelta al mundo real.

title: Infinite Vendetta Part 2
description: Starscream gives Jetfire and Skybyte Spark Armor to escalate their feud and distract everyone from his machinations.

title: Rodeo Parte 1
description: El Caballero por Siempre finalmente reúne a su Mesa Redonda de Caballeros jóvenes pero superpoderosos... i¿incluido Ben?! Con la ayuda de Ben, el Caballero lidera a sus nuevos súbditos en un ataque generalizado contra un acelerador de partículas.

title: You're Everybody's Sidekick
description: KO sets out to prove to Enid that being helpful is rewarding by helping people all around the Lakewood Plaza Turbo.

title: Big Trouble, Little NinjaGo
description: The ninja race to save Lloyd, as a more powerful-than-ever Lord Garmadon creates an enormous Colossi to help him rule Ninjago and defeat the ninja.

title: Pesadilla de verano
description: Drago y los otros Bakugan de Los Fantásticos se enfrentan a una nueva y poderosa amenaza, solo para dejarlos preguntándose si todo habrá sido un sueño.

title: The Mask of Deception
description: When an unknown criminal syndicate threatens the Royal Family, the Ninja are called back into action and must protect the royal princess and a fabled artifact that may hold supernatural powers.

title: Starscream's Children Part 1
description: The Autobots received a distress call from the Nemesis and must come to the aid of their arch-enemies.

title: Wristy Business
description: Beth and Leshawna try to one-up each other with fake injuries as they compete for the attention and sympathy of the other kids at daycare.

title: Gathering Dark
description: Axel must help Bearbarian overcome his secret fear of the dark to stop Dynamo from stealing his ride.

title: The Crossroads Part 2
description: Optimus and the Autobots team up with some very familiar faces to escape Unspace.

title: Una necesidad inquietante
description: La aparición de un nuevo campo Bakugan hace que los chicos del pueblo corran a buscar a sus propios Bakugan. Pero cuando el campo es contaminado, Lia debe salvarlos a todos.

title: #La dulce justicia - Cuarta parte
description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 4 del episodio estreno.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Bonnibel Bubblegum
description: A long lost artifact causes Princess Bubblegum to harken back to the creation of the Candy Kingdom.

title: I Am the Allspark Part 1
description: Starscream successfully merges with the Allspark, spelling doom for the Autobots and Decepticons.

title: Food Truck
description: The Bears open up a food truck after being disappointed by the food options available to them. In an effort to drum up business, they start selling their food to animals until the animals go a little crazy.

title: Rodeo Parte 2
description: El Caballero por Siempre, con una máquina del tiempo a su alcance y un grupo de supermalvados a su lado, está cerca de conquistar toda la historia. Pero cierto héroe con un equipo de 10 alienígenas de su lado tiene otros planes.

title: Secret Science Part 2
description: Wheeljack attempts to break out of the Nemesis while Windblade hunts down Bludgeon to avenge Slipstream.

title: El vagon de la gata
description: Tulip debe enfrentar su pasado.

title: Radio Silence
description: Oscar must get Hedgehog a special sandwich in order to save their friendship.

title: Heroes locales
description: Los Fantásticos provocan una ola de destrucción por accidente, y los padres de Dan se preguntan si deberían permitirle a los niños conservar sus Bakugan.

title: #SweetJustice Part 1
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: First Flight
description: The gang is taking an airplane trip together, and Hawk is at the helm since today he's taking his captain's license test. However Richard is terrified of flying, so Unikitty & Puppycorn spend the chaotic flight trying to help Rick conquer his fear of flying while Dr Fox joins Hawk in the cockpit to help him pass his test. After a destructive and dangerous flight, Rick makes it safetly back on the ground (after surviving the plane crashing). Hawk fails his test but gets to take it again next week, so the gang is excited for another free flight.

title: Duelo de globos
description: Cuando Vic es traicionado durante una guerra de globos de agua, emprende una vengativa misión para descubrir al responsable.

title: The Code
description: Gumball learns the Wattersons have been stealing Mr. Robinson's wi-fi for years. When it goes down, they try and live without it but life offline proves too hard. Gumball and Darwin decide to hack their way through cyberspace to learn Mr Robinson's passcode.

title: Ghost Town Part 2
description: Teletraan-X attempts to rehabilitate Starscream while Optimus, Bee, Hot Rod and Cheetor's quest to save Windblade uncovers a city that is more than meets the eye.

title: Know Your Fusion
description: Steven and the Gems delve deep into what makes a fusion so special.

title: Big Pinchy
description: JP leads his friends on a voyage to find the biggest crayfish in the creek.

title: Bubbles of the Opera
description: When Bubbles gets a bad school photo, it sends her into an existential tailspin of darkness.

title: Trapped in Paradise
description: Unikitty and the gang have crashed on a fabulous island. It's really nice and no one wants to leave until Richard convinces them that they need to return to the Kingdom and deal with their responsibilities. Unfortunately every attempt to escape the island is sabotaged. Now they must find the culprit to ensure their return home.

title: Favorite Shirt
description: Mordecai, Rigby, and High Five Ghost have to somehow get Muscle Man's favorite shirt back on him before he wakes up.

title: Lion 4: Alternate Ending
description: Lion coughs up a magical key, and Steven goes on a quest to find what it unlocks.

title: High Dive
description: Uncle Grandpa helps Samir overcome his paralyzing fear of the high dive.

title: El vagon cromado
description: El grupo se encuentra con una cara familiar en un vagón espejado.

title: Dread on Arrival
description: The ninja appeal to the police commissioner of Ninjago in an effort to help save Lloyd and thwart Harumi's efforts to resurrect the evil Lord Garmadon.

title: Drama Bomb
description: The school play goes off the rails when the drama teacher interferes.

title: Country Club
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to rescue the golf cart from a bunch of rich people at a country club.

title: #LaDulceJusticia - Segunda parte
description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 2 del episodio estreno.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Un verdadero lider
description: Entre diversas amenazas, como el misterioso Shargo Ronin, Dan y Shun no pueden acordar la mejor forma de convertir a Los Fantásticos en un verdadero equipo.

title: Wiped Out Part 1
description: Out in space to catch some solar waves, Bumblebee, Hot Rod and Cheetor discover the asteroid remains of a mysterious planet.

title: Volcano
description: A super-grumpy volcano appears in the kingdom, so Unikitty takes the gang on an epic quest to cheer it up with one of FeeBee's flowers before it erupts and destroys the kingdom.

title: Miedo en la Familia
description: Ben y Gwen están ansiosos por que el Omni-Copter llegue a las Grandes Pirámides. Pero cuando el mal tiempo interrumpe su vuelo, pronto se enfrentan cara a cara con Neblina y sus engendros: iLa familia Niebla!

title: Polos Opuestos
description: Un viaje al Polo Sur queda patas arriba cuando el equipo Tennyson aterriza en el Polo Norte. Pero Ben rápidamente descubre a los culpables: iSolar y Polar Twain, unos científicos con poder magnético que quieren chantajear al mundo amenazando con invertir los polos magnéticos de la Tierra!

title: Sabelotodo
description: Cuando Vic accidentalmente libera malvados murciélagos de una cueva, depende de los chicos y de Don proteger el pueblo, pero la actitud de sabelotodo de Vic pone en peligro la tarea.

title: Big Ben 10
description: Cuando Ben y su familia viajan a Londres para visitar el legendario Big Ben, los hermanos Bicho están allí para darles la bienvenida, obviamente con un nuevo plan escandalosamente exagerado: iencoger la campana del Big Ben para robarla!

title: Coleccionalos todos
description: Después de que los otros Titanes son convertidos en figuras de colección y desaparecen, Robin debe recorrer ventas de garage y tiendas para encontrarlos.

title: Dark Birth Part 2
description: The Autobots and Decepticons battle aboard the Nemesis while Starscream uses the Allspark and Vector Sigma to create new allies.

title: TV Knight 5
description: Batman pretends to be sick to avoid work so he and Commissioner Gordon can run around town watching their favorite shows.

title: Wasted True Potential
description: In the wake of the previous season's victory, the ninja have gone soft and Master Wu must remind them of who they truly are.

title: I Love You Mao Mao
description: An explosive loner and his slacker best friend are waylaid from their journey into legend, only to find that their story is just beginning.

title: No Shortcuts
description: After struggling to keep up, Adorabat gets a cybernetic "Mega-Mech." But can fancy new powers make up for experience?

title: Jerky Jasper
description: Uncle Grandpa goes to great lengths to meet Pizza Steve's imaginary friend.

title: The Oni & the Dragon
description: While Princess Harumi adjusts to life with the ninja, Lloyd and Jay search for answers about the Oni Masks, while Cole and Zane attempt to infiltrate the Sons of Garmadon.

title: Amor a primera mordida
description: A Val le gusta una chica llamada Matty, y Vic sospecha de ella, pero Val ignora sus advertencias. Cuando Val va a su casa a cenar, ella se convierte en una Matlazihua, iy Val descubre que él es la cena!

title: Broke His Crown
description: When Ice King's magic crown goes haywire, Marceline and Princess Bubblegum resort to extreme measures to help him.

title: A Split End
description: After replicating Cut Man's powers, Mega Man goes on a perfectionist spree, putting him on a collision course with Cut Man himself, whose latest stint as a hairdresser hasn't helped him overcome his own compulsions.

title: Huyendo de casa
description: Descubriremos el misterioso pasado de Shun, su relación con su padre (un magnate de la industria), y su deseo por tener una familia más unida.

title: Spotted Part 2
description: Cheetor's scout training with Bee lands them in the clutches of Starscream who tests an evil experiment on them.
